    -- Simpler: provide the factored form directly
    -- 2-6s-6s┬▓-8s┬│ = (1-4s)(2+2s+8s┬▓)/4... let me compute:
    -- (1-4s)(2+2s) = 2+2s-8s-8s┬▓ = 2-6s-8s┬▓. Not quite.
