/-! ### `bch_sextic_term` тАФ the ╧ДтБ╢ coefficient of `bch(a, b)`

Explicit 28-term polynomial in {a, b}, derived via the CAS pipeline at
`Lean-Trotter/scripts/extract_bch_z6.py` (extends `extract_bch_z5.py` to
degree 6). Common denominator 1440; integer numerators in {┬▒1, ┬▒4, ┬▒6, ┬▒24}.
Sum of |numerators|/1440 = 164/1440 тЙИ 0.1139 < 1, so `тАЦZтВЖ(a,b)тАЦ тЙд sтБ╢`.

This is the next term in the BCH expansion after `bch_quintic_term`:
`bch(a,b) = a + b + ┬╜[a,b] + ZтВГ + ZтВД + ZтВЕ + ZтВЖ + O(┬╖^7)`.

Used in the sextic identity (T2-F7e) for canceling deg-6 contributions to
`sym_bch_cubic - sym_EтВГ - sym_EтВЕ`. -/

/-- **╧ДтБ╢ coefficient of `bch(a, b)`** тАФ explicit 28-term polynomial in {a, b}.

The 28 non-zero 6-letter words (out of 64 = 2тБ╢ possible) come from the
free Lie algebra basis at degree 6. Coefficients are rational with LCM 1440. -/
noncomputable def bch_sextic_term (ЁЭХВ : Type*) [RCLike ЁЭХВ] {ЁЭФ╕ : Type*}
    [NormedRing ЁЭФ╕] [NormedAlgebra ЁЭХВ ЁЭФ╕] (a b : ЁЭФ╕) : ЁЭФ╕ :=
    (-1 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * a * a * a * b * b)
  + (4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * a * a * b * a * b)
  + (4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * a * a * b * b * b)
  + (-6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * a * b * a * a * b)
  + (-6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * a * b * a * b * b)
  + (-6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * a * b * b * a * b)
  + (-1 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * a * b * b * b * b)
  + (4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * b * a * a * a * b)
  + (-6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * b * a * a * b * b)
  + (24 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * b * a * b * a * b)
  + (4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * b * a * b * b * b)
  + (-6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * b * b * a * a * b)
  + (-6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * b * b * a * b * b)
  + (4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (a * b * b * b * a * b)
  + (-4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * a * a * a * b * a)
  + (6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * a * a * b * a * a)
  + (6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * a * a * b * b * a)
  + (-4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * a * b * a * a * a)
  + (-24 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * a * b * a * b * a)
  + (6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * a * b * b * a * a)
  + (-4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * a * b * b * b * a)
  + (1 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * b * a * a * a * a)
  + (6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * b * a * a * b * a)
  + (6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * b * a * b * a * a)
  + (6 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * b * a * b * b * a)
  + (-4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * b * b * a * a * a)
  + (-4 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * b * b * a * b * a)
  + (1 / 1440 : ЁЭХВ) тАв (b * b * b * b * a * a)

