/-- **Lipschitz bound for `bch_octic_term`**: `тАЦZтВИ(z, y) тИТ ZтВИ(x, y)тАЦ тЙд 8┬╖MтБ╖┬╖тАЦzтИТxтАЦ`
where `M = тАЦzтАЦ+тАЦxтАЦ+тАЦyтАЦ`.

Analog of `norm_bch_septic_term_diff_le` (session 28) at one degree higher;
the deg-8 BCH coefficient is Lipschitz in its first argument.

With `z = (a'+b) + W` and `тАЦWтАЦ = O(s┬▓)`, gives an O(sтБ╣┬╖тАЦWтАЦ) bound on
`тАЦCтВИ(z, y) тИТ CтВИ(a'+b, y)тАЦ`. Completes the `bch_octic_term` infrastructure
quartet (def + norm bound + vanishing + Lipschitz) for stepping stone 1.

The proof uses a uniform per-i bound `(432/120960) ┬╖ 8 ┬╖ MтБ╖ ┬╖ тАЦzтИТxтАЦ`,
giving `╬г тЙд 124┬╖432┬╖8/120960 = 428544/120960 = 124/35 тЙд 8`. -/
theorem norm_bch_octic_term_diff_le (z x y : ЁЭФ╕) :
    тАЦbch_octic_term ЁЭХВ z y - bch_octic_term ЁЭХВ x yтАЦ тЙд
      8 * (тАЦzтАЦ + тАЦxтАЦ + тАЦyтАЦ) ^ 7 * тАЦz - xтАЦ := by
  set M := тАЦzтАЦ + тАЦxтАЦ + тАЦyтАЦ with hM_def
  have hM_nn : 0 тЙд M := by positivity
  have hz_le : тАЦzтАЦ тЙд M := by
    show тАЦzтАЦ тЙд тАЦzтАЦ + тАЦxтАЦ + тАЦyтАЦ; linarith [norm_nonneg x, norm_nonneg y]
  have hx_le : тАЦxтАЦ тЙд M := by
    show тАЦxтАЦ тЙд тАЦzтАЦ + тАЦxтАЦ + тАЦyтАЦ; linarith [norm_nonneg z, norm_nonneg y]
  have hy_le : тАЦyтАЦ тЙд M := by
    show тАЦyтАЦ тЙд тАЦzтАЦ + тАЦxтАЦ + тАЦyтАЦ; linarith [norm_nonneg z, norm_nonneg x]
  have hM7_nn : 0 тЙд M^7 := pow_nonneg hM_nn 7
  have hzx_nn : 0 тЙд тАЦz - xтАЦ := norm_nonneg _
  rw [bch_octic_term_eq_sum, bch_octic_term_eq_sum, тЖР Finset.sum_sub_distrib]
  calc тАЦтИС i : Fin 124, (bchOcticTerm (ЁЭХВ := ЁЭХВ) z y i - bchOcticTerm (ЁЭХВ := ЁЭХВ) x y i)тАЦ
      тЙд тИС i : Fin 124, тАЦbchOcticTerm (ЁЭХВ := ЁЭХВ) z y i - bchOcticTerm (ЁЭХВ := ЁЭХВ) x y iтАЦ := norm_sum_le _ _
    _ тЙд тИС _i : Fin 124, (432 / 120960 : тДЭ) * 8 * M^7 * тАЦz - xтАЦ :=
        Finset.sum_le_sum (fun i _ => bchOcticTerm_diff_norm_le (ЁЭХВ := ЁЭХВ) z x y M hz_le hx_le hy_le hM_nn i)
    _ = 124 * ((432 / 120960 : тДЭ) * 8 * M^7 * тАЦz - xтАЦ) := by
        rw [Finset.sum_const, Finset.card_univ, Fintype.card_fin]; ring
    _ тЙд 8 * M^7 * тАЦz - xтАЦ := by nlinarith [hM7_nn, hzx_nn]

/-! #### Lipschitz bounds for `bch_sextic_term` per-word тАФ sample (Phase A.2 of T2-F7e)

Per-word Lipschitz bounds: for each 6-letter word `w` in `bch_sextic_term`,
`тАЦw(z, y) тИТ w(x, y)тАЦ тЙд k_w ┬╖ MтБ╡ ┬╖ тАЦzтИТxтАЦ` where `M = тАЦzтАЦ+тАЦxтАЦ+тАЦyтАЦ` and
`k_w` = number of a-positions in w. This sample contains the 4 words with
|coef|=1, demonstrating the technique that scales to all 28 words. -/

