/-- **Fourth-order BCH**: `bch(a,b) = (a+b) + ┬╜[a,b] + bch_cubic_term(a,b) + O(sтБ┤)`.

This extends H1 by identifying the cubic coefficient `(1/12)([a,[a,b]]+[b,[b,a]])`.
The proof extracts the quartic log remainder `logOnePlus(y)-y+┬╜y┬▓-тЕУy┬│` and the
