set_option maxHeartbeats 4000000000 in
include ЁЭХВ in
/-- **Sixth-order BCH remainder, small-s case** (Tier-1 of B1.c).

For `s = тАЦaтАЦ+тАЦbтАЦ < 1/10`: `тАЦLHS_sexticтАЦ тЙд 100┬╖sтБ╢/(2-exp(s))`.

